{"tid":1011910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人狂吃榴槤 竟致馬國雨林爆生態危機","createTime":"2019-02-07T07:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T10:45:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"03b0df4f1184fe3ee681bf627e0b45931d9dd557","tid":1011910,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T07:00:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php1HvDge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php1HvDge.jpg&h=b471557e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馬來西亞為滿足中國市場對榴槤的需求，當局砍伐大量熱帶雨林。（法新社）<br />\n<br />\n2019-02-07 13:49<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕榴槤被稱為「水果之王」，也是中國民眾熱愛的水果。然而馬來西亞為滿足中國市場的需求，間接為當地帶來生態浩劫。環保人士警告，為了種植榴槤樹，馬來西亞當局砍伐大量森林，破壞了當地的生物多樣性。<br />\n<br />\n根據《法新社》報導，中國對榴槤的需求量飆升，吉隆坡農業部公布的數據指出，2018年馬來西亞出口至中國的榴槤，收益高達740萬令吉（約新台幣5,553萬元），是2017年同期的2倍多。因此，許多馬來西亞農民從小型果園轉向大範圍種植，剷除熱帶雨林。如當地的勞勿區（Raub），近日砍伐大量雨林，裸露的山坡上種滿了榴槤幼苗。<br />\n<br />\n有水果攤商表示，馬國最出名的榴槤品種「貓山王」，在北京售價高達800元人民幣（約新台幣3641元），比在馬來西亞買貴上好幾倍，然而中國人不惜代價，只為吃到最頂級的榴槤。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，主要負責榴槤栽種計畫的公司是Ample Harvest Produce，然而當《法新社》記者主動聯繫時，該公司拒絕對消失的雨林發表言論；保護自然遺產組織（PEKA）表示，為種植榴槤，導致越來越多森林被砍伐、生物多樣性喪失，且破壞了大象、老虎、靈長類動物等的重要棲息地，嚴重威脅當地生態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2693077\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2693077&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYJq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=b8b860d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2693077&h=f8c4aef4\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2693077</a>"},{"pid":"1493993a0543a353b0bcf6c7bd8ddb3613f37a9c","tid":1011910,"uid":82068,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:23:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那種做咩都係咁撚麻煩"},{"pid":"ab64c1509b43a24096cd748f1f992aab34791b1a","tid":1011910,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:26:34.000Z","msg":"利害了我的國"},{"pid":"3d833f6e9a3b1f622802f2b6c9224387493e800c","tid":1011910,"uid":46151,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:32:45.000Z","msg":"我覺得問題在於嗰啲無良榴槤商伐林種榴槤喎"},{"pid":"c6df6ed471ec8b1448920bf8870e44821447a0e7","tid":1011910,"uid":226119,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:34:23.000Z","msg":"咁都只不過係馬國既選擇，選擇做中國生意而大量開採熱帶雨林。<br />\n咁樣賴晒中國有啲理虧"},{"pid":"f4caf3ce4669540862e3a9a8350eaf175e2dd244","tid":1011910,"uid":160147,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:42:06.000Z","msg":"開發商係本地公司 又冇中國高層<br />\n環保部門又冇俾中國人收買<br />\n冇議員俾人收買<br />\n<br />\n只係馬國自甘墜落 唔怪得人"},{"pid":"cbeed60f72b45fd51f2374d4b5c9449befaa8aee","tid":1011910,"uid":8011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:43:49.000Z","msg":"中國人食髮菜都搞到自己首都沙塵暴毒陰霾啦。"},{"pid":"19c91fe4856df7f4e4f7c1f223f87d806411ee27","tid":1011910,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:44:40.000Z","msg":"蝗"},{"pid":"4616cedbf72eeaa0c41dfea991590a7ebb5ed3e0","tid":1011910,"uid":1067,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:45:54.000Z","msg":"馬拉自己有問題啦"},{"pid":"a3adb05404fddbe3256c36c89afff4f3ab9c102f","tid":1011910,"uid":85776,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"蝗國人無論去到邊都可以搞到人地國家/地方好似比蝗蟲過境咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a29b4ea56e47b67b7cd4c569d48c4e994cc7014","tid":1011910,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:47:21.000Z","msg":"唔明有咩好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勁臭"},{"pid":"b32fe9116199e51f553d95d47ee63a6b017ed23c","tid":1011910,"uid":23087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:47:38.000Z","msg":"Malaysia is very on999"},{"p